  "title": "📌 Associate Executive, HR (Learning & Development)#HHLT",
  "description": "<p><strong></strong><br />📝 <strong>1-Year Contract</strong></p><p>💼 <strong>Job Details</strong></p><ul><li><p>💰 Salary Up to $2800</p></li><li><p>📍 Location: Jalan Bukit Merah</p></li><li><p>🕘 Working Hours: Monday to Friday (Office Hours)<br /><strong></strong><br /><br /></p></li></ul><h3>🧠 <strong>Job Scope</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Administer and support training activities (nominations, applications, confirmations, payments)</p></li><li><p>Monitor attendance, post-training documentation and funding/claims</p></li><li><p>Prepare course materials and set up in-house training venues</p></li><li><p>Maintain training records, catalogue and learning history in LMS</p></li><li><p>Prepare monthly and ad-hoc training reports<br /><br /><br />🎓 <strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><p>Minimum Diploma in any discipline</p></li><li><p>Prior HR internship or relevant HR experience<br /><br /><br />If interested, please email me at biopharma@recruitexpress.com.sg or telegram @alexgohhl</p><p></p><p>➖</p><p>Alex Goh Hock Leong</p><p>(CEI.No: R1763413 l Recruit Express Pte Ltd (Healthcare & Life Science) | 99C4599)</p></li></ul></li></ul>",
